description:
My friends and I made this stop motion movie for a church conference we go to.  It outlines the story of Samson's life according to the book of Judges in the Bible.  I'll add the credits to the the description later, as they're hard to read in the movie, but the song used during it is Tim Hawkins' parody of Delilah, and some of the sounds are from the video game Minecraft.  If anyone wants to know the technical details of the movie, I can put those up too.  :)  Enjoy!

P.S.  Sorry about the quality of some scenes, I had to compress it down a lot to fit it on YouTube, and it kinda made a few scenes blurry.  My perfectionism hates it, but whatever.
